          <p class="instruct_normal">Caillou loves to create in the kitchen! Kids and grown-ups will enjoy making his favorite recipes together:</p>
          <ul>
           <li type="disc" class="instruct_normal"><a href="#EMP">Empañadas</a></li>
           <li type="disc" class="instruct_normal"><a href="#TOAST">Toasted Pumpkin Seeds</a></li>
           <li type="disc" class="instruct_normal"><a href="#PUMPPIE">Frozen Pumpkin Pie</a></li>
